#1101
Entrance to the Old Forest~
You stand on the edge of the infamous Old Forest.
The Old Forest is rumored to allow travelers to enter, 
only never to return.  Large trees loom overhead, so
think is the canopy that less then a few feet in it is 
completely dark. You wonder if you should turn back or
try your chance in the forest and head southward.
~
